PlayState           *-- "1"     EntityManager           : owns
PlayState           *-- "1"     LevelManager            : owns
PlayState           *-- "1"     GameMode                : owns active mode (Strategy)
EntityManager       *-- "*"     Entity                  : owns & deletes
LevelManager        *-- "0..1"  Level                   : creates & destroys

Soldier             *-- "1"     TransformationState     : owns active state
Soldier             *-- "1"     Direction               : owns facing
Enemy               *-- "1"     EnemyAIState            : owns AI logic
Enemy               *-- "0..1"  Weapon                  : owns weapon
PlayerSoldier       *-- "1"     Inventory               : owns
Inventory           *-- "0..1"  Weapon                  : equipped
Inventory           *-- "1"     Pistol                  : default
Inventory           *-- "1"     Knife                   : melee
Inventory           *-- "1"     Grenade                 : grenade prototype

DamagableEntity     *-- "1"     DamageState             : owns staging state
AmphibiousSlug      *-- "1"     VehicleModeStrategy     : owns active mode
ChainOfDeath        *-- "*"     BehaviourLabel          : label set
ChainOfDeath        *-- "*"     PlayerInputRecord       : input window
FingerprintRecorder *-- "*"     PlayerAction            : recorded actions
UrduAssemblyTerminal *-- "*"    Instruction             : parsed program

EnemySpawner *-- "*"            Enemy : owns master copies
SurvivalLevel       *-- "*"     EnemySpawn              : owns table
SupplyCrate         *-- "0..1"  Weapon                  : contained
SupplyCrate         *-- "0..1"  Grenade                 : contained prototype
CampaignLevel       *-- "1"     NoiseProfile            : owns
CampaignLevel       *-- "*"     TerrainChunk            : owns chunks
Level               *-- "1"     TileMap                 : owns
TileMap             *-- "*"     Tile                    : owns grid
