TerrainChunk        *-- "*"     Tile                    : owns chunk tiles
NoiseProfile        *-- "1"     FractalNoise            : owns
FractalNoise        *-- "1"     PerlinNoise             : owns
BiomeMapper         *-- "1"     AerialBiome             : owns flyweight
BiomeMapper         *-- "1"     PlainsBiome             : owns flyweight
BiomeMapper         *-- "1"     AquaticBiome            : owns flyweight
FlameShot           *-- "0..1"  FireStream              : active stream
