' ============================================================
' DEPENDENCIES
' ============================================================
Weapon              ..> Entity                : creates (fire)
EnemyVehicle        ..> Projectile            : creates
CollisionManager    ..> DamagableEntity       : takeDamage
CollisionManager    ..> DamageSource          : constructs per hit
CollisionManager    ..> Explosion             : reads radius
CollisionManager    ..> AreaHazard            : applies dps
CollisionManager    ..> ShieldedSoldier       : calls blockAttack
CollisionManager    ..> MummyWarrior          : checks fire/explosion rule
CollisionManager    ..> Vehicle               : vehicle vs entity
Collectible         ..> PlayerSoldier         : mutates
HUD                 ..> PlayerSoldier         : reads
HUD                 ..> ScoreManager          : reads score
HUD                 ..> DamageState           : reads hueAlpha()
ScoreManager        ..> Enemy                 : reads scoreValue
NoiseProfileFactory ..> NoiseProfile          : creates
BiomeMapper         ..> NoiseProfile          : reads cutoffs
CampaignLevel       ..> BiomeMapper           : classifies tiles
FatTransformState   ..> PlayerSoldier         : flips magnet
Rocket              ..> Explosion             : spawns on impact
GrenadeProjectile   ..> Explosion             : spawns on impact
FireBombProjectile  ..> FirePool              : spawns on impact
FlameShot           ..> FireStream            : creates
Explosion           ..> Tile                  : destroys via Tile::onExplosion
MummyWarrior        ..> FireDamage            : only fire/explosion kills
MummyWarrior        ..> ExplosionDamage       : only fire/explosion kills
Camera              ..> Entity                : follows
InputHandler        ..> PlayerSoldier         : drives input
InputHandler        ..> PlayerAction          : produces commands
DeathCompositor     ..> EnemySpawner          : tilts weights
RagebaitEngine      ..> EnemySpawner          : downgrades spawns
ChainOfDeath        ..> EnemySpawner          : informs spawner
TimelineManager     ..> Entity                : snapshots state
Paratrooper         ..> Infantry              : morphs into on landing
UltimateBoss        ..> IronNokana            : delegates ground attack
UltimateBoss        ..> HairBusterRiberts     : delegates aerial attack
UltimateBoss        ..> SeaSatan              : delegates aquatic attack
Martian             ..> EnergyBeam            : fires in phase 1
RainSystem          ..> TileMap               : fills craters
RainSystem          ..> WaterTile             : creates new water tiles
POWPrisoner         ..> SupplyCrate           : spawns on release
Bullet              ..> PlayerSoldier         : Fannum Tax bending
BossLevel           ..> Boss                  : manages boss phases
MenuState           ..> MainMenu              : reads selection
MenuState           ..> GameMode              : assigns to PlayState
Zombie              ..> Weapon                : uses pistol
SoundManager        ..> WaterTile             : checks submersion
PlayState           ..> VoiceActivationEngine : startup trigger
NEATManager         ..> PlayState             : runs simulation
Genome              ..> PlayState             : evaluates fitness
UrduAssemblyTerminal ..> PlayerSoldier        : modifies stats
UrduAssemblyTerminal ..> ScoreManager         : modifies score
UrduAssemblyTerminal ..> Instruction          : creates per line
EnemySpawner        ..> Level                 : spawns into level
FingerprintAutopilot ..> PlayerAction         : replays commands
Inventory           ..> Grenade               : clones prototype on throw

